---
title: Activity Diagram - Pencatatan Transaksi Keuangan
---
flowchart TD
    Start([Sumber Transaksi]) --> Source{Jenis<br/>Transaksi?}
    Source -->|Pendapatan| Income[Booking / Service Charge]
    Source -->|Pengeluaran| Outflow[Operasional / Inventory]
    Source -->|Deposit| Deposit1[Deposit Tamu]

    Income --> InvCreate[Generate Invoice via /billing]
    InvCreate --> InsertInv[INSERT INTO invoices]
    InsertInv --> InsertItems[INSERT INTO billing_items]
    InsertItems --> WaitPay[Status: Pending Payment]
    WaitPay --> PaymentIn[Tamu Bayar]
    PaymentIn --> RecordPayment[INSERT INTO payments status='confirmed']
    RecordPayment --> UpdateInv[UPDATE invoice status='paid']
    UpdateInv --> Report

    Outflow --> CreateExp[Buat Expense via /financial]
    CreateExp --> InsertExp[INSERT INTO expenses category, amount]
    InsertExp --> Approve{Butuh<br/>Approval?}
    Approve -->|Ya| ManagerApp[Manager Setujui]
    Approve -->|Tidak| Recorded
    ManagerApp --> Recorded[Status: Recorded]
    Recorded --> Report

    Deposit1 --> InsertDep[INSERT INTO deposits collected_by]
    InsertDep --> HoldFunds[Saldo Ditahan Sistem]
    HoldFunds --> CheckoutTime{Check-out<br/>Tamu?}
    CheckoutTime -->|Ya| Refund{Ada<br/>Kerusakan?}
    Refund -->|Tidak| FullRefund[UPDATE refunded_by + Refund Penuh]
    Refund -->|Ya| PartialRefund[UPDATE refunded_by + Refund Sebagian]
    FullRefund --> Report
    PartialRefund --> Report

    Report[Generate Laporan di /reports] --> End([Selesai])

    classDef startEnd fill:#c8e6c9,stroke:#2e7d32,color:#000
    classDef decision fill:#fff9c4,stroke:#f57f17,color:#000
    classDef action fill:#bbdefb,stroke:#1565c0,color:#000
    classDef income fill:#dcedc8,stroke:#558b2f,color:#000
    classDef outflow fill:#ffccbc,stroke:#d84315,color:#000
    classDef deposit fill:#b3e5fc,stroke:#01579b,color:#000
    class Start,End startEnd
    class Source,Approve,CheckoutTime,Refund decision
    class Income,InvCreate,InsertInv,InsertItems,WaitPay,PaymentIn,RecordPayment,UpdateInv income
    class Outflow,CreateExp,InsertExp,ManagerApp,Recorded outflow
    class Deposit1,InsertDep,HoldFunds,FullRefund,PartialRefund deposit
    class Report action
